{"tid":2218813,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"奈及利亞13歲男童罵神被判10年刑 聯合國關切","createTime":"2020-09-26T12:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T13:16:00.000Z","uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e257322d2671197b8c7732afda69875a72dc4970","tid":2218813,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T12:59:56.000Z","msg":"奈及利亞近日傳出爭議判決，一名13歲男童因為用言語褻瀆神明，結果被判10年有期徒刑，聯合國兒童基金會對此表示關切。<br />\n<br />\n《CNN》報導，奈及利亞以褻瀆罪判處一名13歲男童10年有期徒刑，聯合國兒童基金會（UNICEF）對此做出譴責。13歲的法魯克（Omar Farouq）被指控跟朋友吵架時，用言語褻瀆阿拉，結果被判刑，日前有另一名男子因為褻瀆先知莫罕默德，被同一名法官判處死刑。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，法魯克的律師表示，這起判決違反了《非洲兒童權利與福利憲章》，並於7日提出上訴，律師指出，褻瀆神明並未列入奈及利亞的法律。聯合國兒童基金會也對此表示深切關注，直言將一個13歲的孩子判處10年徒刑是錯誤的，呼籲該國政府撤銷判決。"},{"pid":"29b11a75c5f80b995035c70725cc883ad20adc47","tid":2218813,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T13:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023f98a0230303d8858e97dbf4895037a0fc580f","tid":2218813,"uid":201604,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T13:00:35.000Z","msg":"阿拉都係幫我含撚咋"},{"pid":"057bdecbf2c5e151e7c5c797004d85ceb41d6010","tid":2218813,"uid":531,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T13:01:30.000Z","msg":"中國拆十字架改聖經嘅時候聯合國呢"},{"pid":"15a9e99fc31a7f37e822edd83c326f47d464fe53","tid":2218813,"uid":71213,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"057bdecbf2c5e151e7c5c797004d85ceb41d6010","tid":2218813,"uid":531,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T13:01:30.000Z","msg":"中國拆十字架改聖經嘅時候聯合國呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T13:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjbzeau